# Optional: left unset, the app derives the API URL from whatever host you're
# viewing the page on (localhost or your LAN IP) plus the backend's default
# port 4000, so it works automatically from both a desktop browser and a
# phone on the same network. Set this explicitly only for production, where
# the API typically lives on a different domain.
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
